WEBVTT

00:37.000 --> 00:40.666
<i>In the name of Allah,
the Most Gracious and the Most Merciful.</i>

00:41.750 --> 00:48.083
<i>Whatever affliction befalls you is because
of what your own hands have committed.</i>

00:48.791 --> 00:51.208
<i>And He pardons much.</i>

00:52.458 --> 00:54.958
Din, look at my new toy.

00:55.041 --> 00:56.166
Where is it?

01:00.250 --> 01:01.333
It's here.

01:02.791 --> 01:04.083
Try and turn it on.

01:06.333 --> 01:08.833
- Look. Isn't it funny?
- Whoa.

01:10.041 --> 01:11.458
This is mine.

01:11.541 --> 01:13.291
- It's mine.
- Eykha, give it back.

01:13.375 --> 01:14.250
It's mine.

01:14.333 --> 01:15.791
Cheers, everyone!

01:15.875 --> 01:17.833
Eykha! Give it back!

01:18.875 --> 01:20.333
Eykha.

01:21.625 --> 01:22.833
Eykha.

01:25.666 --> 01:28.083
- Why are you playing this here?
- Come on.

01:28.750 --> 01:30.375
Do you realize what time it is?

01:30.458 --> 01:31.291
Go upstairs.

01:32.333 --> 01:33.291
Yusoff.

01:35.166 --> 01:38.208
Eykha, go to your room.

01:38.750 --> 01:40.708
Change into your pyjamas.

01:40.791 --> 01:42.291
I'll be there soon.

01:43.583 --> 01:45.500
- Neng.
- Yes, Ma'am.

01:46.500 --> 01:50.458
Please take Eykha and Yusoff to their room
and prepare them for bed.

01:51.083 --> 01:52.000
Yes, Ma'am.

01:52.541 --> 01:55.916
Neng, take the milk for the kids.

01:56.000 --> 01:57.666
I made extra for Din.

01:58.500 --> 01:59.958
Thank you, Ma'am.

02:00.583 --> 02:03.708
Yusoff, let's go to bed. Come.

02:06.958 --> 02:08.708
- Din, let's go upstairs.
- Okay.

02:10.041 --> 02:11.708
What a funny looking monkey.

02:12.875 --> 02:15.208
- It has small ears.
- Just like mine.

02:18.625 --> 02:20.250
It has pearly white teeth.

02:23.125 --> 02:24.833
Where did your dad get them?

02:24.916 --> 02:26.291
Overseas.

02:27.416 --> 02:28.875
Was it expensive?

02:28.958 --> 02:30.000
I don't know.

02:31.791 --> 02:33.916
I'm sure it's expensive.

02:34.000 --> 02:36.666
You're lucky to get a toy like this.

02:36.750 --> 02:37.791
Its nose.

02:38.625 --> 02:40.000
Ears and teeth.

02:40.750 --> 02:41.958
- Its hands.
- And teeth.

02:42.666 --> 02:45.791
Din, that's enough. Stop playing.

02:45.875 --> 02:47.333
But, Mother...

02:47.416 --> 02:49.166
I said stop.

02:49.250 --> 02:50.750
Go to bed.

02:51.416 --> 02:52.708
Come on.

02:54.500 --> 02:56.791
It's okay, Din.
You can have it for the night.

02:56.875 --> 02:59.291
Just return it to me in the morning, okay?

03:00.000 --> 03:01.791
- Are you serious?
- Yes.

03:02.750 --> 03:04.708
- Are you sure?
- Yes.

03:05.208 --> 03:06.958
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

03:09.666 --> 03:11.541
- Good night.
- Good night.

03:24.833 --> 03:27.000
Sleep, Sweetheart. Have sweet dreams.

03:27.583 --> 03:29.333
You are my heart and soul.

03:29.416 --> 03:31.416
I love you, Eykha.

03:37.625 --> 03:39.666
You are my heart and soul too.

03:40.458 --> 03:42.291
I love you, Yusoff.

03:48.833 --> 03:49.875
Yusoff.

03:51.333 --> 03:52.583
Take care of your sister.

03:53.541 --> 03:54.875
Try not to fight so often.

04:24.208 --> 04:25.208
Take this.

04:27.791 --> 04:29.041
Eykha!

04:51.000 --> 04:52.166
Peace be upon you.

04:52.250 --> 04:53.416
<i>And upon you be peace.</i>

04:54.833 --> 04:56.791
- Have you arrived?
<i>- Yes.</i>

04:56.875 --> 04:59.166
<i>I was held back
by immigration for some time.</i>

04:59.250 --> 05:00.125
Huh?

05:00.833 --> 05:01.833
Why?

05:02.416 --> 05:03.375
I don't know.

05:04.833 --> 05:06.416
Maybe it's because
I've been away for so long.

05:07.708 --> 05:08.958
It has been 30 years.

05:09.041 --> 05:10.750
<i>Mom, is that Dad?</i>

05:10.833 --> 05:11.833
Is that Mikhail?

05:13.083 --> 05:14.125
Let me talk to him.

05:15.708 --> 05:16.583
Dad.

05:17.375 --> 05:20.291
Mikhail, how was school today?

05:20.375 --> 05:22.000
<i>We learned</i> ayatul kursi <i>today.</i>

05:22.583 --> 05:24.250
Our teacher wants to hear
the recitation next week.

05:24.333 --> 05:25.375
<i>Let me hear it.</i>

05:26.791 --> 05:30.833
<i>In the name of Allah, the Most Gracious
and Most Merciful. Allah!</i>

05:30.916 --> 05:33.041
<i>There is no god worthy of worship
except Him,</i>

05:33.125 --> 05:35.125
<i>the Ever-Living, All-Sustaining.</i>

05:35.208 --> 05:36.333
<i>Neither...</i>

05:36.416 --> 05:38.166
<i>No...</i>

05:38.250 --> 05:39.250
It's too hard, Dad.

05:39.333 --> 05:41.541
It's okay. You can memorize it slowly.

05:42.208 --> 05:43.708
God willing, you can do it.

05:43.791 --> 05:45.041
<i>Let me talk to your mother.</i>

05:45.125 --> 05:46.000
Okay, Dad.

05:46.083 --> 05:48.916
<i>- Peace be upon you.</i>
- And upon you be peace.

05:49.000 --> 05:51.708
Honey, don't you want me to be there?

05:52.625 --> 05:55.208
There's no need. I've told you that.

05:55.291 --> 05:59.833
This might be the first and last time
I'll get the chance to see your father.

05:59.916 --> 06:02.833
Besides, I'm sure
Mikhail wants to see his grandpa.

06:02.916 --> 06:04.291
Which part of no, don't you understand?

06:04.375 --> 06:05.583
<i>Huh?</i>

06:05.666 --> 06:09.250
<i>I don't want you and Mikhail
to get involved with this family.</i>

06:09.333 --> 06:11.125
My father is on his deathbed.

06:11.208 --> 06:13.125
I'm only coming home to handle his burial.

06:13.208 --> 06:14.083
<i>O Allah.</i>

06:14.666 --> 06:15.583
Yusoff!

06:16.791 --> 06:18.291
How could you say that?

06:18.375 --> 06:20.916
<i>No matter what he did,
he is still your father.</i>

06:21.583 --> 06:22.708
Okay.

06:22.791 --> 06:24.708
<i>I'll call you if anything comes up.</i>

06:24.791 --> 06:26.083
<i>Send my love to Mikhail.</i>

06:26.166 --> 06:28.333
<i>- Peace be upon you.</i>
- And upon you be peace.

06:37.083 --> 06:38.500
How much further, Pak Mat?

06:40.250 --> 06:41.416
We're almost there.

06:42.416 --> 06:43.625
Is everything...

06:46.000 --> 06:47.041
still the same?

06:49.208 --> 06:53.375
In this world,
nothing stays the same forever, Yusoff.

06:54.583 --> 06:57.041
The young will age.

06:57.791 --> 07:00.625
The living will die.

07:01.208 --> 07:03.791
Those who left, like you,

07:04.625 --> 07:06.166
will eventually return.

07:08.875 --> 07:10.000
Yes.

07:17.166 --> 07:19.708
The difference is in
how you live your life.

07:20.333 --> 07:21.541
Do you choose to do good

07:22.708 --> 07:23.958
or bad in this life?

08:35.916 --> 08:36.833
Take this.

08:37.416 --> 08:40.458
Only one bag? And it's small too.

08:40.541 --> 08:42.166
He won't have enough clothes.

08:42.250 --> 08:43.541
I can carry that myself.

08:43.625 --> 08:45.708
No, it's okay.

09:12.625 --> 09:13.750
No!

09:14.500 --> 09:17.208
That's not right.

09:19.083 --> 09:20.791
You play it every day.

09:20.875 --> 09:23.333
How can you still get it wrong?

09:31.875 --> 09:33.083
Eykha.

09:33.708 --> 09:35.833
Don't touch me.

09:35.916 --> 09:37.041
Go away.

09:42.458 --> 09:43.541
I'm your brother, Yusoff.

09:45.416 --> 09:49.500
What brings you home so suddenly?

09:52.541 --> 09:53.541
Leave.

09:53.625 --> 09:55.083
Eykha.

09:56.291 --> 09:58.041
I came home for you.

09:58.125 --> 10:00.625
Mom doesn't want

10:01.208 --> 10:03.500
- you here.
- Mom?

10:03.583 --> 10:05.791
Eykha.

10:05.875 --> 10:09.375
- Eykha, does Mom keep in touch with you?
- Don't touch me!

10:09.458 --> 10:10.833
Did Mom contact you?

10:11.500 --> 10:13.875
Mom is no longer here.

10:14.791 --> 10:16.583
She ran away.

10:17.125 --> 10:20.500
Just like how you ran away
and left me here.

10:20.583 --> 10:22.166
- Eykha.
- In this house,

10:22.250 --> 10:25.708
- only the people I despise remain.
- Eykha.

10:25.791 --> 10:29.000
- Don't touch me!
- Eykha!

10:53.166 --> 10:54.791
Eykha is unwell.

10:56.500 --> 11:00.750
Her condition worsened after Nur ran away.

11:04.708 --> 11:05.958
Mak War?

11:08.375 --> 11:10.708
I'm glad you came home.

11:12.250 --> 11:15.375
He wants to see his favourite son
before he passes.

11:18.083 --> 11:19.083
Listen, Yusoff.

11:20.833 --> 11:22.708
Go to your room first.

11:24.125 --> 11:26.166
When your father wakes up,

11:29.125 --> 11:30.750
I will call for you.

11:56.166 --> 11:58.708
Hey!

11:58.791 --> 12:01.333
Didn't I tell you to put your toys away?

12:01.416 --> 12:03.000
Are you still not done playing?

12:03.083 --> 12:04.333
Cheeky kids.

12:04.416 --> 12:06.375
This is what you get for shooting me.

12:06.458 --> 12:08.083
Are you going to shoot me again?

12:47.625 --> 12:48.791
Take it.

12:54.958 --> 12:55.958
Hey!

12:58.125 --> 12:59.541
What are you doing here?

13:00.708 --> 13:02.458
This is not your room anymore.

13:03.500 --> 13:05.583
You can sleep downstairs.

13:05.666 --> 13:09.833
In the housekeeper's quarters.

13:17.166 --> 13:18.041
Yusoff.

13:19.958 --> 13:21.291
Your father is awake.

13:21.875 --> 13:23.833
- You may see him now.
- Okay.

14:23.000 --> 14:23.958
Don't.

14:25.083 --> 14:27.041
Your father doesn't like the lights.

14:27.125 --> 14:29.458
His eyes hurt if it's too bright.

14:50.416 --> 14:52.083
Peace be upon you, Dad.

14:53.958 --> 14:54.958
It's me, Yusoff.

15:00.291 --> 15:02.250
I've stayed away from you for a long time.

15:06.416 --> 15:07.833
Away from this family.

15:14.333 --> 15:15.916
I only want to know...

15:18.708 --> 15:20.458
why did you send me away?

15:26.250 --> 15:28.875
I often asked myself...

15:32.000 --> 15:33.000
why?

15:40.791 --> 15:42.458
What did I do wrong?

15:50.208 --> 15:51.875
Why did Mom run away?

15:58.458 --> 16:01.625
Why hasn't anyone in this house
tried to contact me?

16:12.250 --> 16:14.208
I need to know the answers.

16:18.875 --> 16:19.875
Why?

16:23.291 --> 16:26.625
How could you and Mom...

16:50.375 --> 16:51.375
Dad.

17:03.000 --> 17:04.666
Dad.

17:05.333 --> 17:06.541
Dad.

17:07.875 --> 17:09.625
Dad, say your shahada.

17:10.666 --> 17:12.375
Dad, say your shahada.

17:13.250 --> 17:15.208
<i>I bear witness
that there is no god but Allah</i>

17:15.291 --> 17:17.625
<i>and I bear witness that
Muhammad is the messenger of Allah.</i>

17:17.708 --> 17:20.583
<i>Dad, say your shahada. I bear witness
that there is no god but Allah</i>

17:20.666 --> 17:23.125
<i>and I bear witness that
Muhammad is the messenger of Allah.</i>

17:23.208 --> 17:26.250
Say your shahada, Dad. Please.

17:29.500 --> 17:30.416
Dad?

18:15.708 --> 18:16.791
Five.

18:16.875 --> 18:17.958
Four.

18:18.041 --> 18:19.208
Three.

18:19.291 --> 18:20.375
Two.

18:20.458 --> 18:21.708
One.

18:43.916 --> 18:45.541
Are you ready?

18:51.000 --> 18:52.458
I found you!

18:52.958 --> 18:54.458
You're so good at this.

18:54.541 --> 18:57.083
This house is huge.
How did you manage to find me?

19:28.625 --> 19:30.083
Yusoff.

20:08.000 --> 20:09.708
I seek forgiveness from Allah.

20:16.041 --> 20:17.666
Next time, pay then you can come.

20:19.583 --> 20:20.583
Take it, Yusoff.

20:28.333 --> 20:30.833
What were you doing in there?

20:31.708 --> 20:34.666
Were you playing hide and seek?

20:35.333 --> 20:37.583
Why didn't you ask me to play with you?

20:46.750 --> 20:49.250
In the name of Allah.

20:59.125 --> 21:00.125
Is it good?

21:02.916 --> 21:03.833
Yes.

21:03.916 --> 21:06.291
Better than your late mother's cooking?

21:07.916 --> 21:09.250
What do you mean?

21:10.875 --> 21:12.500
No one can replace my mother.

21:12.583 --> 21:15.458
Of course, she has her own cooking style.

21:16.666 --> 21:18.708
No one can top her.

21:18.791 --> 21:20.500
But what can you do about it?

21:20.583 --> 21:22.583
She left her children.

21:22.666 --> 21:25.458
Mom is here.

21:26.416 --> 21:29.250
She never left us.

21:29.333 --> 21:34.708
I just met her yesterday, under the tree.

21:39.041 --> 21:40.625
Anyway, you're teaching in Cairo?

21:41.833 --> 21:43.916
Yes, I am.

21:44.000 --> 21:46.208
Islamic Philosophy and Culture.

21:48.083 --> 21:50.541
I'm sure you love traditional elements.

21:51.250 --> 21:53.125
Age-old customs

21:53.625 --> 21:56.916
must be taught to our descendants.

21:57.000 --> 21:58.791
We must preserve it.

21:59.291 --> 22:02.708
I prepared chicken feet soup for you.

22:12.291 --> 22:13.375
Try it.

22:25.833 --> 22:26.750
Good, isn't it?

22:26.833 --> 22:28.583
No!

22:28.666 --> 22:31.625
I don't want to eat! I want Mom!

22:34.041 --> 22:35.833
My goodness.

22:38.416 --> 22:40.833
- I'm sorry, Sir. She's often like this.
- Neng.

22:40.916 --> 22:43.833
- Yes, Ma'am.
- Give her her medicine.

22:44.708 --> 22:47.625
- Milk with honey I made earlier.
- Yes, Ma'am.

22:48.333 --> 22:49.958
What is she taking, Mak War?

22:50.041 --> 22:51.750
Tranquilizers.

22:52.375 --> 22:54.750
To help control her outbursts.

22:54.833 --> 22:57.833
Her doctor advised
that she should be hospitalized.

22:59.333 --> 23:01.083
I won't allow it.

23:01.166 --> 23:03.833
I don't trust modern medicine.

23:10.291 --> 23:14.166
<i>The number you dialed cannot be reached.</i>

26:21.791 --> 26:24.291
<i>There is no god but Allah.</i>

26:24.375 --> 26:28.375
<i>Glory be to Allah.
I have certainly done wrong.</i>

26:31.500 --> 26:35.500
<i>There is no god but Allah.
Glory be to Allah.</i>

27:11.750 --> 27:15.125
I seek forgiveness from Allah Almighty.

27:34.375 --> 27:35.791
A bit tired.

27:43.750 --> 27:45.583
Yusoff prefers not to travel

27:47.041 --> 27:48.958
since Mikhail was born.

27:51.208 --> 27:54.291
So when I heard Father has fallen ill,

27:55.125 --> 27:56.875
I really wanted to meet...

27:59.666 --> 28:01.083
Honey.

28:01.166 --> 28:02.375
What are you doing here?

28:08.458 --> 28:09.666
Let's go upstairs.

28:11.041 --> 28:12.500
- Mikhail. Hey.
- Dad.

28:18.166 --> 28:23.666
Mikhail, do you want
to see my toys in my room?

28:24.208 --> 28:25.208
Let's go.

28:25.958 --> 28:28.125
My daughter-in-law is beautiful.

28:30.083 --> 28:31.583
You have good taste.

28:39.833 --> 28:40.916
What is the matter?

28:44.541 --> 28:45.833
Why did you come here?

28:46.916 --> 28:48.291
Why did you bring Mikhail?

28:48.375 --> 28:51.041
I told you not to come!

28:53.375 --> 28:55.083
I wanted to surprise you.

28:56.291 --> 28:59.333
I thought you'd be happy
if I brought Mikhail too.

28:59.416 --> 29:00.458
Marissa,

29:01.083 --> 29:03.541
how many times
have I told you I didn't want you

29:03.625 --> 29:05.333
and our son near this family?

29:07.208 --> 29:09.666
Yes, I know.

29:09.750 --> 29:12.333
There's no point
in talking about this anymore.

29:12.416 --> 29:14.375
I'm here now.

29:14.458 --> 29:16.208
I want to meet your father.

29:16.291 --> 29:19.166
And this might be my first
and last chance to do that.

29:19.250 --> 29:22.750
Or are you embarrassed by me so
you're keeping me from your father?

29:22.833 --> 29:24.083
I'm your wife.

29:24.166 --> 29:28.583
As your wife, I think I should know
how my husband is feeling,

29:28.666 --> 29:30.833
and what he is thinking and doing.

29:30.916 --> 29:32.458
That's what marriage is.

29:33.208 --> 29:34.541
We communicate.

29:34.625 --> 29:35.833
Not doing everything alone!

29:35.916 --> 29:38.416
So because I always kept to myself

29:39.291 --> 29:40.666
you had an affair?

29:40.750 --> 29:42.083
Is that your excuse?

29:42.625 --> 29:44.041
You need attention from other men?

29:48.666 --> 29:49.666
Yusoff.

30:01.583 --> 30:02.708
Marissa.

30:04.416 --> 30:05.416
Hey.

30:11.083 --> 30:12.500
I'm sorry, okay?

30:18.000 --> 30:19.333
My intention

30:20.666 --> 30:22.750
was only to meet your family.

30:23.875 --> 30:25.500
Especially your father.

30:27.958 --> 30:30.250
You know I don't have a family, Yusoff.

30:30.333 --> 30:33.916
You and your family
are the only family I have.

30:34.500 --> 30:36.000
I hope you understand.

30:39.833 --> 30:41.041
I understand.

30:43.583 --> 30:45.791
But after our business here is done,

30:46.958 --> 30:48.375
we go home.

30:58.791 --> 31:00.125
Peace be upon you, Dad.

31:00.875 --> 31:03.750
I want to introduce my wife to you.

31:13.916 --> 31:15.375
Peace be upon you, Father.

31:20.916 --> 31:21.916
Come here, Sweetheart.

31:25.041 --> 31:28.250
Father, this is our son.

31:28.333 --> 31:29.875
His name is Mikhail.

31:49.416 --> 31:50.875
Say your shahada, Dad.

31:50.958 --> 31:54.000
Snake...

31:55.958 --> 31:59.250
Say your shahada, Dad.
Dad, say your shahada.

31:59.333 --> 32:02.166
<i>I bear witness
that there is no god but Allah</i>

32:02.250 --> 32:04.833
<i>and I bear witness that
Muhammad is the messenger of Allah.</i>

32:04.916 --> 32:08.250
<i>I bear witness there is no god but Allah</i>

32:08.333 --> 32:13.125
<i>and I bear witness that
Muhammad is the messenger of Allah.</i>

32:13.208 --> 32:14.333
Say your shahada, Dad.

32:20.208 --> 32:21.333
Dad.

32:22.916 --> 32:23.916
Dad.

32:25.833 --> 32:26.708
Dad.

32:28.291 --> 32:29.708
Pak Mat.

32:40.333 --> 32:43.291
<i>Indeed, we belong to Allah
and to Him we shall return.</i>

32:54.750 --> 32:58.416
<i>In the name of Allah,
the Most Gracious and the Most Merciful.</i>

33:08.875 --> 33:12.083
<i>This is a revelation
from the Almighty, Most Merciful...</i>

33:13.083 --> 33:15.083
- Take this Ya-Sin book.
- Thank you.

33:15.166 --> 33:17.708
Make sure you practice
reading Chapter Ya-Sin.

33:17.791 --> 33:19.458
- Thank you.
- My condolences.

33:20.458 --> 33:22.833
It's okay to be slow,
but make sure you keep practicing.

33:22.916 --> 33:24.583
- You'll improve over time.
- My condolences.

33:24.666 --> 33:26.000
- Thank you.
- My condolences.

33:27.250 --> 33:29.500
- Go eat at the back.
- Okay, Dad.

33:32.916 --> 33:34.625
- Pak Mat.
- Yusoff.

33:35.375 --> 33:38.625
I've talked to the funeral committee.

33:39.166 --> 33:41.208
The sun is setting.

33:41.291 --> 33:44.000
Let's settle
your father's burial tomorrow morning.

33:44.791 --> 33:45.625
Okay.

33:46.875 --> 33:50.250
I need to go to the mosque
to organise the <i>tahlil</i>

33:50.333 --> 33:53.333
and invite the congregation
to come tomorrow.

33:53.916 --> 33:55.250
- Yes, Pak Mat.
- Okay.

34:13.791 --> 34:19.583
<i>In the name of Allah,
the Most Gracious and the Most Merciful.</i>

34:21.583 --> 34:26.958
<i>Allah! There is no god
worthy of worship except Allah...</i>

34:27.041 --> 34:29.291
Do you want some, Mikhail?

34:29.958 --> 34:31.125
My mom said I can't.

34:34.041 --> 34:37.541
That used to be your dad's bed.

34:37.625 --> 34:42.958
He was the same age you are now.

34:45.666 --> 34:49.208
And then, he left me.

34:50.500 --> 34:54.875
I stayed in this house

34:54.958 --> 34:57.916
all alone.

34:58.000 --> 35:01.000
I had no friends.

35:03.166 --> 35:04.958
Do you have friends?

35:05.541 --> 35:07.083
My schoolmates.

35:12.958 --> 35:16.333
How fun. You can attend school?

35:19.041 --> 35:21.416
I never got to go to school.

35:23.041 --> 35:24.958
I have no friends.

35:25.791 --> 35:29.125
Will you be my friend, Mikhail?

35:39.500 --> 35:40.958
I'm not alone.

35:46.875 --> 35:48.708
I have my mom.

36:16.958 --> 36:18.125
Darling.

36:23.750 --> 36:25.791
I owe you an apology.

36:28.666 --> 36:32.875
I've said things that I shouldn't

36:34.375 --> 36:35.916
when you arrived earlier.

36:54.291 --> 36:57.416
I hope you know
that I love you and our son.

37:07.250 --> 37:08.916
One more thing.

37:11.958 --> 37:17.000
We have to book our flight home soon.

37:30.166 --> 37:32.416
- I'm sorry, Darling.
- Yusoff.

37:35.958 --> 37:37.416
Who are you talking to?

37:44.708 --> 37:46.125
Where were you?

37:47.208 --> 37:48.958
I went downstairs to check up on Mikhail.

37:50.041 --> 37:52.416
And then, I had coffee with Mak War.

37:58.958 --> 37:59.958
Yusoff,

38:03.750 --> 38:04.750
Mak War looks so young.

38:10.666 --> 38:12.916
When you left this house,

38:14.250 --> 38:16.250
did she look the same as she does now?

38:18.666 --> 38:20.500
I don't really remember.

38:22.666 --> 38:23.875
This family...

38:26.041 --> 38:27.166
practices something.

38:30.041 --> 38:32.666
Let's get some sleep.
I'll tell you more about it later.

39:20.500 --> 39:23.833
<i>I don't want to eat! I want Mom!</i>

40:07.791 --> 40:09.541
Where's the fuse box?

42:37.125 --> 42:38.250
Yusoff!

42:39.416 --> 42:40.958
Why did you come home?

42:45.916 --> 42:46.916
What are you doing over there, Sir?

42:55.875 --> 42:57.541
I seek the forgiveness of Allah.

43:05.041 --> 43:07.791
This is an old neighbourhood.

43:07.875 --> 43:09.708
Sometimes, we don't have power at all.

43:15.291 --> 43:16.375
This house...

43:20.333 --> 43:21.541
I don't know what to say.

43:25.166 --> 43:26.166
Good grief!

43:28.625 --> 43:30.916
Neng, open the door.

43:31.000 --> 43:32.833
Gosh, it was him.

43:37.333 --> 43:38.958
- What happened, Pak Mat?
- Eykha!

43:39.041 --> 43:41.000
I seek forgiveness from Allah, the Mighty.

43:42.666 --> 43:44.666
Pak Mat, how did Eykha end up outside?

43:45.583 --> 43:48.791
- Eykha?
- I was looking for Mom.

43:48.875 --> 43:51.041
- What were you looking for?
- Neng.

43:51.125 --> 43:52.541
Take Eykha to her room.

43:52.625 --> 43:54.791
Help her wash up and
give her some milk with honey.

43:54.875 --> 43:57.291
- And then, tuck her in.
- Yes, Sir.

43:57.375 --> 43:59.291
Why do you keep doing this?

43:59.375 --> 44:01.500
You do this almost every week.

44:04.458 --> 44:06.916
Pak Mat, what happened?

44:20.958 --> 44:21.916
Eykha.

44:25.833 --> 44:26.750
Eykha.

44:31.583 --> 44:32.458
Eykha.

44:33.916 --> 44:34.916
Eykha.

44:38.708 --> 44:41.291
It doesn't matter if the doors are locked.

44:41.375 --> 44:43.250
She still finds ways to go out.

44:45.583 --> 44:48.333
Why didn't my late father
get her treated, Pak Mat?

44:51.041 --> 44:54.375
Mak War keeps giving her milk with honey.

44:54.458 --> 44:56.375
She said she could treat her.

44:56.458 --> 44:58.166
What else could I say?

44:59.208 --> 45:01.083
What was Eykha doing there?

45:02.458 --> 45:04.291
What's under that tree?

45:05.750 --> 45:07.375
She said she was looking for Mom.

45:08.416 --> 45:10.125
She was sleep-walking, Yusoff.

45:10.708 --> 45:12.791
She didn't know where she was going.

45:13.916 --> 45:16.541
Enough. We have to wake up early.

45:16.625 --> 45:18.708
We must bury your father.

45:19.375 --> 45:20.500
Get some sleep.

45:35.333 --> 45:37.291
INDEED, WE BELONG TO ALLAH
AND TO ALLAH WE SHALL RETURN

45:51.666 --> 45:55.333
Blood. Help get me out. Allah is Great.

45:56.375 --> 45:59.458
Imam, blood keeps seeping out. Look.

46:05.833 --> 46:07.083
What do we do?

46:07.166 --> 46:10.208
No matter what, we have to do our duty.

46:11.375 --> 46:12.541
What do we do, Yusoff?

46:13.708 --> 46:16.583
It's okay, Imam.
Let me go down and finish the task.

46:19.291 --> 46:21.250
<i>Oh Allah, send blessings upon Muhammad.</i>

46:22.791 --> 46:24.541
<i>Allah is Greater.</i>

46:24.625 --> 46:27.333
<i>- In the name of Allah.</i>
- Excuse me, Brother.

46:27.416 --> 46:28.666
Please give way.

46:28.750 --> 46:30.166
<i>In the name of Allah.</i>

46:31.541 --> 46:32.416
Hold his head.

46:37.333 --> 46:39.416
Please hand me the board.

46:42.666 --> 46:44.125
- Slowly.
- Do you have it?

46:49.875 --> 46:53.041
<i>I seek refuge in Allah
from the accursed Satan.</i>

46:53.125 --> 46:55.833
<i>Every soul will taste death.</i>

46:55.916 --> 46:59.958
<i>And you will only receive your full reward
on the Day of Judgment.</i>

47:00.041 --> 47:02.541
<i>Whoever is spared from the Fire</i>

47:02.625 --> 47:05.291
<i>and is admitted into Paradise
will indeed triumph</i>

47:05.375 --> 47:07.125
<i>whereas the life of this world...</i>

47:07.208 --> 47:12.125
Whatever affliction befalls you is because
of what your own hands have committed.

47:12.916 --> 47:15.791
And He pardons much.

47:22.666 --> 47:25.916
Whatever befalls you from some hardship

47:27.958 --> 47:30.583
is because of your own hands.

47:31.875 --> 47:35.375
And Allah pardons most of your major sins.

47:36.000 --> 47:37.333
Let's go.

47:43.708 --> 47:46.958
Marissa, do you have relatives here?

47:52.083 --> 47:53.208
We're estranged.

47:56.333 --> 47:59.708
And my parents both passed away

48:00.291 --> 48:02.500
when I was nineteen.

48:03.125 --> 48:04.291
What happened?

48:05.375 --> 48:06.500
It was an accident.

48:09.500 --> 48:10.875
At that time,

48:11.833 --> 48:15.708
I was studying in the UK
and I couldn't get home in time.

48:16.291 --> 48:18.833
I met Yusoff around the same time.

48:24.500 --> 48:28.708
My parents gave up so much for me.

48:32.291 --> 48:36.500
But I couldn't repay them.

48:43.750 --> 48:44.750
I'm sorry.

48:45.333 --> 48:46.875
I don't know what's come over me.

48:49.500 --> 48:53.125
So when Yusoff told me he was coming home

48:53.208 --> 48:57.416
to visit his sick and dying father,

48:58.583 --> 49:00.375
my heart broke.

49:01.458 --> 49:03.208
I was reminded of my parents.

49:03.791 --> 49:06.166
That's what parents do, Marissa.

49:06.250 --> 49:08.208
You're a mother now.

49:09.041 --> 49:11.166
I'm sure you can understand them better.

49:11.791 --> 49:13.750
My life isn't much different
from yours, Marissa.

49:17.083 --> 49:19.416
<i>The fire spread so quickly.</i>

49:20.083 --> 49:23.291
<i>I didn't have time to save anything.</i>

49:23.375 --> 49:26.916
<i>I didn't have time to save my parents.</i>

49:27.583 --> 49:30.083
<i>One second later</i>

49:30.166 --> 49:33.291
<i>and I would've been
consumed by the fire too.</i>

49:34.208 --> 49:37.000
<i>But fate had another thing
in store for me.</i>

49:38.458 --> 49:41.250
<i>Yusoff's father came and rescued me.</i>

49:43.041 --> 49:45.416
<i>He appeared out of nowhere</i>

49:46.375 --> 49:49.291
<i>and made me his wife.</i>

49:50.708 --> 49:53.250
<i>The late Ghazali was a good man</i>

49:53.958 --> 49:55.333
<i>and he was rich.</i>

49:56.291 --> 49:58.583
<i>Of course he already
had a woman in his life.</i>

49:59.708 --> 50:01.916
<i>Nur was pregnant with Eykha at that time.</i>

50:04.250 --> 50:06.875
<i>She was hesitant about me at first.</i>

50:09.500 --> 50:12.625
<i>Perhaps the marriage
brought blessings into our lives.</i>

50:13.583 --> 50:15.583
<i>Ghazali's wealth continued to grow.</i>

50:16.250 --> 50:18.500
<i>But I assured her</i>

50:19.000 --> 50:22.166
<i>I didn't come to steal her husband away.</i>

50:23.166 --> 50:26.958
<i>I only wanted to share their happiness.</i>

50:30.625 --> 50:33.500
We as women, must stay strong.

50:34.208 --> 50:35.875
We must endure.

50:36.625 --> 50:38.750
Marissa, call me Mother.

50:46.833 --> 50:49.375
- Dad, I want to sit here.
- Huh?

50:51.291 --> 50:54.791
- Okay. Don't wander off.
- Okay.

51:33.166 --> 51:34.458
Yusoff.

51:38.333 --> 51:40.208
Yusoff, what's the matter?

51:41.458 --> 51:42.500
Pack our bags.

51:43.500 --> 51:45.166
We have to leave this house and go home.

51:47.958 --> 51:48.916
What's going on?

51:49.000 --> 51:50.333
This is too sudden.

51:51.041 --> 51:52.166
Marissa.

51:52.916 --> 51:55.166
Marissa, please listen to me this once.

51:55.250 --> 51:56.541
I...

51:59.250 --> 52:00.416
Listen to you?

52:02.833 --> 52:04.000
Yusoff?

52:06.583 --> 52:07.791
Yusoff.

52:09.708 --> 52:10.875
Yusoff, what's wrong?

52:20.125 --> 52:21.916
This house is haunted, Marissa.

52:24.208 --> 52:26.541
Because you brought Mikhail here,
that spirit has become more...

52:26.625 --> 52:28.041
More what?

52:33.208 --> 52:34.625
What are you doing, Mikhail?

52:46.208 --> 52:47.541
Let's play ball.

52:48.458 --> 52:49.791
Yusoff.

52:50.583 --> 52:54.166
- Yusoff, I'm talking to you!
- Can we talk about this later?

52:55.083 --> 52:56.166
Later.

52:56.875 --> 52:58.916
But now, you have to get Mikhail.

52:59.000 --> 53:00.583
Get Mikhail.

53:01.500 --> 53:04.958
Me? You want me to bring Mikhail here?

53:05.041 --> 53:07.666
You want nothing to do with him, do you?

53:09.833 --> 53:10.833
Take it.

53:19.291 --> 53:21.750
Okay. Look, Mikhail.

53:23.583 --> 53:25.458
Oh, no.

53:25.541 --> 53:27.166
- Can you bring the ball, Mikhail?
- Yes.

53:30.916 --> 53:33.625
Yusoff. Will you talk to me?

53:37.750 --> 53:38.916
Yusoff.

53:39.916 --> 53:42.708
Are you listening to me? Yusoff.

53:44.583 --> 53:46.333
How long will you punish me?

53:48.875 --> 53:49.875
Yusoff.

53:58.375 --> 53:59.958
What is wrong with you?

54:00.833 --> 54:02.583
Are you running away again?

54:02.666 --> 54:04.458
Yusoff, you're no longer a kid!

54:04.541 --> 54:07.041
You ran away from this house once.
Now you're running again?

54:07.125 --> 54:11.000
Excuse me.
I didn't run away, I was sent away.

54:12.083 --> 54:15.375
What do you want now?
So you're trying to control me now?

54:15.458 --> 54:17.958
And pretending like you've
been putting up with everything?

54:18.041 --> 54:18.958
Yes!

54:20.041 --> 54:21.125
You're right!

54:22.833 --> 54:24.750
The things you did to me, Marissa.

54:24.833 --> 54:27.500
Would any other husband
forgive you the way I did?

54:27.583 --> 54:28.583
Yusoff!

54:29.250 --> 54:31.375
Don't you...

54:38.708 --> 54:41.166
- Mikhail!
- Mikhail?

54:41.250 --> 54:42.375
Mikhail!

54:44.000 --> 54:45.791
- Mikhail.
- Mikhail.

54:47.083 --> 54:48.708
- Mikhail.
- Mikhail.

54:48.791 --> 54:51.583
- Mikhail.
- Mikhail.

54:51.666 --> 54:53.625
- Eykha, what happened?
- Sweetheart.

54:53.708 --> 54:55.500
Let's bring him in for now.

54:55.583 --> 54:57.166
Mikhail, what's wrong?

55:04.333 --> 55:06.291
- Mikhail, wake up.
- Mikhail.

55:06.375 --> 55:07.541
- Mikhail.
- Mikhail.

55:08.416 --> 55:10.291
- Mikhail, my boy.
- Mikhail.

55:10.375 --> 55:11.958
Mikhail, wake up.

55:12.041 --> 55:13.791
- Mikhail.
- Mikhail.

55:13.875 --> 55:15.833
- Mikhail. Wake up, Sweetheart.
- Mikhail.

55:17.250 --> 55:19.791
He's burning up. Marissa, grab your phone
and call the ambulance.

55:19.875 --> 55:22.791
- Mikhail.
- What happened?

55:22.875 --> 55:24.541
Marissa, your phone!

55:24.625 --> 55:26.000
Hey, Mikhail.

55:28.458 --> 55:29.833
Mikhail passed out, Mother.

55:31.083 --> 55:32.375
Mikhail.

55:36.125 --> 55:37.625
Pak Mat, let's take him to the hospital.

55:37.708 --> 55:38.791
Wait.

55:40.250 --> 55:41.833
He needs rest.

55:41.916 --> 55:43.375
Try not to move him around.

55:45.458 --> 55:47.083
Let me heal him.

55:47.166 --> 55:49.666
He needs a doctor, not a Shaman.

55:49.750 --> 55:50.833
Yusoff.

55:52.916 --> 55:54.416
How will you treat him?

55:55.125 --> 55:56.291
Key lime? Incense?

55:56.375 --> 55:59.208
Yusoff, don't talk to your mother
like that.

55:59.291 --> 56:01.541
- She is not...
- Let's wait the night.

56:02.416 --> 56:04.291
If his fever hasn't subsided by tomorrow,

56:05.208 --> 56:06.291
we'll go to the hospital.

56:07.375 --> 56:08.500
Okay, Mother.

56:18.750 --> 56:20.958
Mikhail. Wake up, sweetheart.

56:40.833 --> 56:42.375
Don't worry.

56:42.458 --> 56:44.458
I heal people all the time.

56:48.541 --> 56:50.083
Praise be to Allah.

56:53.666 --> 56:54.875
My son.

57:04.708 --> 57:05.791
Let him get some rest.

57:08.958 --> 57:12.083
If anything comes up, you can call me.

57:21.125 --> 57:22.333
He's still running a fever.

57:24.875 --> 57:26.000
Marissa, don't call her Mother.

57:26.583 --> 57:27.583
Besides, she has nothing to do...

57:27.666 --> 57:30.083
I don't want us to argue
in front of Mikhail.

57:43.875 --> 57:46.125
It's good that he came to.

57:46.750 --> 57:49.250
Perhaps he was not used to a new place.

57:50.500 --> 57:51.666
This house.

57:56.000 --> 57:57.208
This land.

58:00.416 --> 58:02.416
I think that was the cause, Pak Mat.

58:04.875 --> 58:06.125
It's haunted.

58:11.166 --> 58:13.500
This house, this land

58:14.125 --> 58:16.625
are occupied by humans, Yusoff.

58:17.708 --> 58:21.750
What the humans living in this house
and on this land do

58:22.583 --> 58:26.125
is what invited the spirits to reside.

58:31.500 --> 58:32.625
Pak Mat.

58:34.708 --> 58:36.250
Do you have the keys to the basement?

58:39.750 --> 58:42.666
No, only Mak War has them.

58:42.750 --> 58:45.250
- Why do you want to enter the room?
- Never mind.

58:46.333 --> 58:47.500
I only want to take a look inside.

58:48.625 --> 58:51.125
There's nothing inside for you to look at.

58:51.833 --> 58:53.833
That room has become a storage area.

58:54.750 --> 58:56.208
I organized it myself.

59:02.166 --> 59:03.500
Is it true?

59:05.875 --> 59:07.333
After I went away...

59:09.250 --> 59:10.875
did they still practise polytheism?

59:10.958 --> 59:13.583
Dear Allah. Yusoff.

59:16.291 --> 59:18.125
That's an old story.

59:19.291 --> 59:20.625
I already told you.

59:20.708 --> 59:21.875
Pak Mat.

59:22.958 --> 59:24.625
Who else can I ask these questions to?

59:24.708 --> 59:27.708
I spent my last days here with you.

59:37.958 --> 59:39.666
Where are we going?

59:41.541 --> 59:43.958
Yusoff, once we arrive at the airport,

59:44.041 --> 59:47.333
a friend of your fathers
will take you to London, okay?

59:47.916 --> 59:49.083
Where's my mom?

59:49.583 --> 59:53.166
Your mother will meet you at the airport.

01:00:04.000 --> 01:00:07.083
Your father ordered me to get you out.

01:00:08.333 --> 01:00:10.416
I was only following orders, Yusoff.

01:00:10.500 --> 01:00:12.833
You told me
my mom would come to the airport.

01:00:13.583 --> 01:00:15.583
Why wasn't she there, Pak Mat?

01:00:15.666 --> 01:00:16.833
She ran away.

01:00:16.916 --> 01:00:20.791
According to your father, she left
that morning before I sent you away.

01:00:21.666 --> 01:00:23.541
We still don't know where she went.

01:00:25.958 --> 01:00:27.333
Why would she run away?

01:00:28.750 --> 01:00:30.208
Was she upset with Mak War?

01:00:33.500 --> 01:00:38.666
Yusoff, we're holding a <i>tahlil</i> for
your late father at the mosque tonight.

01:00:39.541 --> 01:00:43.791
- Come with me.
- But my son, Pak Mat.

01:00:44.541 --> 01:00:48.750
Come on. Sick children
look for their mother, not their father.

01:00:49.583 --> 01:00:51.041
Ride with me.

01:01:00.666 --> 01:01:01.958
Come in.

01:01:08.375 --> 01:01:10.458
How is Mikhail?

01:01:13.166 --> 01:01:14.875
He's still sleeping, Eykha.

01:01:14.958 --> 01:01:16.958
I'm sorry.

01:01:19.000 --> 01:01:22.625
I don't know what happened earlier.

01:01:23.583 --> 01:01:25.541
Mak War is upset with me.

01:01:26.208 --> 01:01:28.500
I have to go to bed.

01:01:29.208 --> 01:01:30.708
Good night.

01:01:34.916 --> 01:01:35.916
Eykha, wait a minute.

01:01:38.666 --> 01:01:41.583
I'm going to the mosque.
We're holding a <i>tahlil</i> tonight.

01:01:44.416 --> 01:01:46.250
What is it?

01:01:52.833 --> 01:01:53.958
Eykha.

01:01:55.166 --> 01:01:56.750
I want to apologize.

01:01:57.916 --> 01:01:59.750
I pushed you aside earlier.

01:02:03.166 --> 01:02:04.291
My brother Yusoff.

01:02:06.208 --> 01:02:10.916
You're the only person
I have in this world now.

01:02:14.916 --> 01:02:17.458
Mom is no longer around.

01:02:21.458 --> 01:02:23.375
You left.

01:02:27.708 --> 01:02:29.416
I have to live in this house...

01:02:32.833 --> 01:02:34.583
Alone.

01:02:35.750 --> 01:02:37.166
It gets lonely

01:02:39.875 --> 01:02:42.458
to live without love.

01:02:49.625 --> 01:02:51.583
You have them.

01:02:56.166 --> 01:03:01.208
You don't feel sad, do you?

01:03:03.750 --> 01:03:05.791
You don't feel lonely.

01:03:10.666 --> 01:03:14.958
If you came home

01:03:15.041 --> 01:03:18.833
to add grief to my heart,

01:03:19.625 --> 01:03:23.291
I think you better leave.

01:03:31.375 --> 01:03:33.583
Peace be upon you.

01:03:52.125 --> 01:03:53.208
Mom!

01:05:01.666 --> 01:05:02.666
Mom!

01:05:04.625 --> 01:05:05.666
Mikhail.

01:05:06.458 --> 01:05:08.250
What's wrong, Sweetheart?

01:05:10.958 --> 01:05:12.458
I...

01:05:21.083 --> 01:05:23.083
There's nothing there, Sweetie. Come.

01:05:23.166 --> 01:05:24.291
Let's go back to sleep.

01:05:27.875 --> 01:05:28.916
Get more sleep, okay?

01:05:29.958 --> 01:05:31.791
You're still running a fever.

01:05:32.708 --> 01:05:34.375
Rest your body. Here.

01:06:43.541 --> 01:06:45.708
<i>Ya-sin.</i>

01:06:45.791 --> 01:06:48.916
<i>By the Quran, rich in wisdom!</i>

01:06:49.000 --> 01:06:52.583
<i>Indeed you, Oh Muhammad,
are from among the messengers</i>

01:06:52.666 --> 01:06:55.541
<i>upon the Straight Path.</i>

01:07:58.625 --> 01:07:59.875
Mother.

01:07:59.958 --> 01:08:01.000
Marissa.

01:08:02.750 --> 01:08:03.750
What's all this, Mother?

01:08:03.833 --> 01:08:05.666
Join us for dinner.

01:08:07.833 --> 01:08:11.041
My relatives dropped by
to have a little feast.

01:08:12.500 --> 01:08:16.416
This is how we celebrate
Ghazali's passing.

01:08:17.416 --> 01:08:19.791
I'm very grateful

01:08:19.875 --> 01:08:23.166
to receive so much love
in such a trying time.

01:08:25.958 --> 01:08:27.000
Let me go.

01:08:44.916 --> 01:08:46.208
Yusoff!

01:08:46.708 --> 01:08:47.625
Mikhail!

01:08:47.708 --> 01:08:48.916
Yusoff!

01:08:49.000 --> 01:08:50.708
Mikhail!

01:08:51.333 --> 01:08:52.958
Yusoff!

01:08:54.750 --> 01:08:56.750
Yusoff!

01:09:00.125 --> 01:09:02.250
It has been 30 years
since I was last home.

01:09:05.750 --> 01:09:07.250
Sorry to have kept you waiting, Pak Mat.

01:09:10.666 --> 01:09:14.208
The congregation asked me to give a talk
after the Fajr prayer tomorrow.

01:09:14.291 --> 01:09:17.083
I'm not an Islamic studies professor.

01:09:17.166 --> 01:09:21.208
I told them I could only
give them a talk on Islamic history.

01:09:23.666 --> 01:09:25.041
Let's go, Pak Mat.

01:09:57.916 --> 01:09:59.583
I've been thinking

01:10:00.375 --> 01:10:03.791
about what I should do
now that your father has passed.

01:10:05.791 --> 01:10:07.625
You can get another job, Pak Mat.

01:10:09.791 --> 01:10:11.375
You're free now.

01:10:11.458 --> 01:10:12.875
Freedom?

01:10:14.041 --> 01:10:16.333
That word doesn't come cheap.

01:10:20.166 --> 01:10:21.875
I was never free.

01:10:33.708 --> 01:10:36.500
<i>Mak War came into your father's life</i>

01:10:36.583 --> 01:10:39.916
<i>and made him even more wealthy
and powerful.</i>

01:10:40.000 --> 01:10:43.291
<i>She had control over everyone.</i>

01:10:44.083 --> 01:10:46.000
<i>You mother had doubts,</i>

01:10:46.083 --> 01:10:49.750
<i>but Mak War's black magic
was too powerful.</i>

01:10:50.833 --> 01:10:52.125
That night,

01:10:52.208 --> 01:10:53.500
<i>they sacrificed Din.</i>

01:10:55.291 --> 01:11:01.458
The life of one boy for every blood moon.

01:11:01.541 --> 01:11:05.000
You weren't supposed to be there.

01:11:13.250 --> 01:11:17.416
<i>I had to obey MaWar
because I became her slave.</i>

01:11:17.500 --> 01:11:21.083
<i>Or else, she would take my life too.</i>

01:11:21.166 --> 01:11:22.750
He saw us.

01:11:22.833 --> 01:11:25.250
Let's hear what Mawar has to say first.

01:11:25.333 --> 01:11:27.458
Yusoff must die.

01:11:28.583 --> 01:11:32.541
Don't let our feelings
get in the way, Nur.

01:11:33.166 --> 01:11:36.166
You came into my home.

01:11:36.250 --> 01:11:38.166
You took my husband.

01:11:39.375 --> 01:11:41.333
You used me.

01:11:42.416 --> 01:11:44.583
Now you want to kill my son?

01:11:44.666 --> 01:11:45.833
You...

01:11:49.041 --> 01:11:51.791
<i>Your mother was trying to save you.</i>

01:11:51.875 --> 01:11:55.125
<i>But your father's hands were tied.</i>

01:11:57.541 --> 01:11:59.083
Because he knew

01:12:00.458 --> 01:12:03.000
we had to keep it a secret.

01:12:04.458 --> 01:12:07.125
We had to destroy all the evidence.

01:12:13.958 --> 01:12:18.500
Your mother's life had to be sacrificed,
in exchange for your life.

01:12:18.583 --> 01:12:21.375
That is the reason you're still alive.

01:12:22.625 --> 01:12:24.625
I was the one who buried her that night.

01:12:25.416 --> 01:12:26.625
<i>In the front yard of the house,</i>

01:12:27.291 --> 01:12:29.541
<i>where Eykha always spends her time.</i>

01:12:32.500 --> 01:12:33.750
<i>The very next day,</i>

01:12:34.666 --> 01:12:36.625
<i>you were sent away.</i>

01:12:36.708 --> 01:12:39.541
<i>You are my heart and soul too.</i>

01:12:39.625 --> 01:12:41.416
<i>I love you, Yusoff.</i>

01:12:41.500 --> 01:12:43.333
So you'd be far from all this.

01:12:43.416 --> 01:12:45.958
I'm sorry, Yusoff.

01:12:57.083 --> 01:12:58.500
Yusoff.

01:13:00.791 --> 01:13:02.083
Yusoff.

01:13:03.583 --> 01:13:05.041
I know

01:13:05.625 --> 01:13:09.000
there's no use in apologizing now, but

01:13:10.250 --> 01:13:12.833
you have to know the truth.

01:13:12.916 --> 01:13:16.291
I can't carry this secret any longer.

01:13:18.500 --> 01:13:20.083
Maybe you don't remember,

01:13:20.166 --> 01:13:25.750
but there were other boys before Din
they had sacrificed, Yusoff.

01:13:25.833 --> 01:13:28.166
And more died after you left.

01:13:30.291 --> 01:13:31.916
What are you waiting for?

01:13:32.000 --> 01:13:33.791
Hit me.

01:13:34.541 --> 01:13:35.875
I deserve to be...

01:13:40.791 --> 01:13:42.333
You're a murderer.

01:13:42.416 --> 01:13:45.958
You're no different
from the people in that house.

01:13:47.375 --> 01:13:48.250
Your son.

01:13:49.666 --> 01:13:51.708
Go and save him.

01:14:55.166 --> 01:14:57.458
Mikhail! Marissa!

01:15:05.000 --> 01:15:06.625
<i>Dear Allah.</i>

01:15:09.416 --> 01:15:10.583
Marissa?

01:15:12.791 --> 01:15:15.333
Marissa! Marissa!

01:15:16.833 --> 01:15:18.791
Neng!

01:15:19.375 --> 01:15:20.958
What happened? Where's everyone?

01:15:21.041 --> 01:15:24.625
I don't know.
I think Madam Mawar took them away!

01:15:24.708 --> 01:15:27.208
- Neng, leave this house and never return.
- Okay.

01:15:27.291 --> 01:15:29.083
- Report this to the police.
- Okay.

01:15:29.166 --> 01:15:30.291
Tell the police.

01:15:30.375 --> 01:15:31.708
Mikhail!

01:15:32.666 --> 01:15:34.083
Marissa!

01:17:19.791 --> 01:17:22.041
I'm sorry, Nur.

01:17:22.125 --> 01:17:26.791
I regret doing that to you.

01:17:26.875 --> 01:17:28.750
I'm sorry, Nur.

01:17:48.083 --> 01:17:51.208
<i>I bear witness
that there is no god but Allah</i>

01:17:51.291 --> 01:17:52.958
<i>and I bear witness that
Muhammad is the messenger of Allah.</i>

01:18:18.500 --> 01:18:19.416
Yusoff.

01:18:21.333 --> 01:18:22.416
Marissa.

01:18:29.958 --> 01:18:31.041
Mikhail.

01:18:31.125 --> 01:18:32.708
Mikhail.

01:18:32.791 --> 01:18:34.166
Don't worry about him.

01:18:37.083 --> 01:18:40.750
Ghazali left all his assets
and this house to me.

01:18:43.041 --> 01:18:47.541
But his biggest asset lies in this room.

01:18:50.916 --> 01:18:52.125
What are you saying?

01:18:52.208 --> 01:18:53.416
Our guardian.

01:18:55.666 --> 01:18:57.208
The one that gives us wealth.

01:18:58.000 --> 01:19:00.875
The one that ensures I live till now.

01:19:02.041 --> 01:19:04.708
You were surprised too
when you first saw me, right?

01:19:06.125 --> 01:19:09.000
I was the one
who made your father call you.

01:19:09.083 --> 01:19:11.458
I am dying.

01:19:13.708 --> 01:19:15.125
<i>You're finally home.</i>

01:19:15.208 --> 01:19:17.666
<i>Yusoff, come home.</i>

01:19:19.458 --> 01:19:20.708
You polytheist!

01:19:22.083 --> 01:19:24.208
You're associating with the devil!

01:19:24.291 --> 01:19:28.041
I might be a polytheist to you,
but I've found pleasure.

01:19:32.000 --> 01:19:34.666
You don't know what awaits us.

01:19:35.666 --> 01:19:36.708
Yusoff.

01:19:37.500 --> 01:19:38.458
Mikhail.

01:19:40.208 --> 01:19:44.041
A life of luxury under his protection.

01:20:46.458 --> 01:20:48.416
Mak War! Mikhail!

01:20:52.583 --> 01:20:55.375
Leave him alone, Mak War. Kill me instead.

01:20:55.458 --> 01:20:56.750
You can't kill Ghazali's descendant.

01:20:58.708 --> 01:21:00.083
That is his grandson!

01:21:04.250 --> 01:21:06.166
Grandson?

01:21:21.000 --> 01:21:24.500
It looks like you have no idea.

01:21:24.583 --> 01:21:26.333
Marissa.

01:21:26.416 --> 01:21:29.666
Tell Yusoff the truth.

01:21:30.916 --> 01:21:33.458
Tell him who Mikhail is.

01:21:34.916 --> 01:21:35.833
Marissa.

01:21:37.166 --> 01:21:40.875
What is Mikhail's real identity?

01:21:41.875 --> 01:21:42.833
Marissa.

01:21:51.708 --> 01:21:53.583
What is she talking about?

01:21:54.708 --> 01:21:56.166
Mikhail...

01:22:00.875 --> 01:22:02.666
Mikhail is not your son.

01:22:09.333 --> 01:22:10.583
Yusoff.

01:22:12.333 --> 01:22:14.166
Yusoff, I'm sorry.

01:22:15.000 --> 01:22:16.458
Yusoff.

01:22:17.041 --> 01:22:19.375
I love you.

01:22:20.708 --> 01:22:22.166
Yusoff.

01:22:23.333 --> 01:22:25.500
Take a look around, Yusoff.

01:22:26.833 --> 01:22:29.458
People betray you left and right.

01:22:36.833 --> 01:22:40.708
You only have this mother of yours now.

01:22:44.250 --> 01:22:50.041
You can live in this house with me.

01:22:50.666 --> 01:22:53.125
Yusoff, stay with God.

01:22:53.208 --> 01:22:54.375
Remember Allah.

01:23:06.625 --> 01:23:10.041
- Yusoff.
- Stay with me, Yusoff.

01:23:10.625 --> 01:23:13.041
You are my son.

01:23:14.208 --> 01:23:16.750
Snake...

01:23:19.166 --> 01:23:20.458
Yusoff.

01:23:21.250 --> 01:23:22.583
Yusoff.

01:23:22.666 --> 01:23:24.333
My son.

01:24:27.333 --> 01:24:28.625
Mikhail.

01:24:29.666 --> 01:24:30.708
Mikhail, open your eyes.

01:24:32.125 --> 01:24:33.500
Mikhail. Wake up, my son.

01:24:33.583 --> 01:24:34.750
Come on.

01:24:35.333 --> 01:24:36.291
Where are we?

01:24:36.375 --> 01:24:37.750
- Mikhail.
- Yusoff!

01:24:44.541 --> 01:24:46.916
<i>Allah! There is no god
worthy of worship except Him,</i>

01:24:47.000 --> 01:24:48.916
<i>the Ever-Living, All-Sustaining.</i>

01:24:49.000 --> 01:24:51.916
<i>Neither drowsiness
nor sleep overtakes Him.</i>

01:24:52.708 --> 01:24:55.666
<i>To Him belongs whatever is in the heavens
and whatever is on the earth.</i>

01:24:55.750 --> 01:24:59.958
<i>Who could possibly intercede with Him
without His permission?</i>

01:25:00.500 --> 01:25:04.375
<i>He fully knows what is ahead of them
and what is behind them,</i>

01:25:04.458 --> 01:25:09.625
<i>but no one can grasp any of His knowledge
except what He wills to reveal.</i>

01:25:09.708 --> 01:25:13.791
<i>His Seat encompasses
the heavens and the earth,</i>

01:25:13.875 --> 01:25:16.333
<i>and the preservation of both
does not tire Him.</i>

01:25:16.416 --> 01:25:18.750
<i>For He is the Most High, the Greatest.</i>

01:25:27.000 --> 01:25:30.458
<i>This is a discharge from all obligations,
by Allah and His Messenger,</i>

01:25:30.541 --> 01:25:34.583
<i>to the polytheists you believers
have entered into treaties with.</i>

01:26:27.375 --> 01:26:28.666
Let's go, Marissa.

01:26:40.416 --> 01:26:42.083
- Marissa.
- Huh?

01:26:42.166 --> 01:26:43.750
Marissa. Start Pak Mat's car. Quickly!

01:26:43.833 --> 01:26:46.833
- Where are you going?
- I can't leave Eykha.

01:26:47.791 --> 01:26:49.875
- Hurry.
- Yusoff!

01:26:53.541 --> 01:26:55.083
Eykha.

01:27:18.000 --> 01:27:20.375
Yusoff!

01:27:20.958 --> 01:27:22.333
Allahu Akbar!

01:27:22.416 --> 01:27:24.833
Yusoff!

01:27:31.708 --> 01:27:32.833
Eykha, wake up now.

01:27:32.916 --> 01:27:34.541
We'd got to get out of this house now.

01:27:36.958 --> 01:27:38.750
Just a bit more...

01:27:39.333 --> 01:27:40.250
Eykha.

01:27:41.000 --> 01:27:42.708
Get in, quickly.

01:29:07.458 --> 01:29:10.125
A WOMAN WAS ARRESTED

01:29:10.208 --> 01:29:16.208
A WOMAN'S BODY HAS BEEN FOUND,
THE BOY HAS NOT YET BEEN FOUND.

01:29:18.166 --> 01:29:24.875
TWO BODIES OF 7-YEAR-OLD BOYS FOUND
